# Documentation rules

- Keep root `AGENTS.md` under ~80 lines; link to `docs/` for depth.
- Use kebab-case filenames; ADRs use `NNNN-short-title.md`.
- Prefer links over duplicating content across files.
- Update `docs/workflow/current-tasks.md` when task status changes.
- Mermaid diagrams are fine for architecture and workflow docs.
